1
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:25,159
Take care, young master.

2
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:25,799
Safe travels.

3
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,200
No need to see me out. Please stay.

4
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,120
Hey, Lao Gao.

5
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:29,920
Stop shoving me.

6
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:30,959
Ning Zi!

7
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,519
Get over here.

8
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,079
Tell me.

9
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:35,840
What did you do to my Yudie?

10
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:41,239
Exactly what you're thinking.

11
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,519
He's a complete animal.

12
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,480
Don't!

13
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,159
Don't stop me.

14
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,599
I'm settling this with him once and for all.

15
00:01:51,719 --> 00:01:52,359
Him and me...

16
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,200
Lao Gao.

17
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,079
You want to measure up against him?

18
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:56,480
You think you stand a chance?

19
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,719
All right, all right, all right.

20
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,400
You're out.

21
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:19,919
Didn't sleep all night.

22
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,120
That impressive, huh?

23
00:02:22,919 --> 00:02:23,639
Not bad.

24
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:29,560
How'd it go with Miss Nanzhi?

25
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,360
Sanniang already told me everything.

26
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,759
Our boss here

27
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,639
sat upright the entire night,

28
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,319
till Miss Nanzhi dozed off waiting.

29
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:39,680
Lao Pan.

30
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:42,159
Is there something

31
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,479
seriously wrong with you?

32
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:45,800
You're the sick one.

33
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,560
You're sick.

34
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,240
You're the one with issues.

35
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,039
Until I'm sure Miss Nanzhi

36
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:51,360
actually has feelings for me,

37
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:53,319
I won't lay a finger on her.

38
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,719
Aren't you worried Miss Nanzhi

39
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:55,759
might doubt her own charm?

40
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,000
Aren't you worried Miss Nanzhi

41
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,080
might suspect there's something

42
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,680
physically wrong with you?

43
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:03,159
Would she?

44
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:04,280
Really?

45
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:04,960
She would.

46
00:03:11,159 --> 00:03:14,879
This is the Music Bureau.

47
00:03:15,759 --> 00:03:17,479
What do men come here for?

48
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,919
The girls know perfectly well.

49
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:21,360
Playing innocent at a time like this

50
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:23,159
would be too hypocritical.

51
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,080
I'll go explain.

52
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,560
Brothers, let's go!

53
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,319
Fourth Young Master!

54
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,039
Fourth Young Master! Fourth Young Master!

55
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:33,879
Fourth Young Master!

56
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,400
Fourth Young Master, we meet again!

57
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:35,919
Fourth Young Master!

58
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:37,280
You two fellow beggars,

59
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,879
the kindness of a piece of cloth back then,

60
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,360
I shall never forget.

61
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:43,280
For you.

62
00:03:44,199 --> 00:03:45,400
So much money! So much money!

63
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:46,639
I knew it!

64
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,159
Come to the capital and beg,

65
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,639
and a meteoric rise awaits.

66
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,719
Thank you, Fourth Young Master!

67
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,759
Fourth Young Master,

68
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,919
we have two other brothers

69
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,120
who'd like to meet you.

70
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,120
Yes, yes!

71
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,479
Brother.

72
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:59,680
I've seen many heroes of the world,

73
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,520
but your carefree grace stands above all.

74
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:06,800
A man of fire and valor true,

75
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:11,879
a model hero for us all.

76
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,120
I'm Xing He.

77
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,000
I'm Wu Xian.

78
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:19,680
Pleased to meet you, Fourth Young Master.

79
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:23,199
Xing He, Wu Xian.

80
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:23,879
Fine names.

81
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,639
Fine names indeed.

82
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,199
Meeting is fate.

83
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,920
What troubles you two?

84
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,600
Well, Fourth Young Master,

85
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,360
we came all this way

86
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,360
just to

87
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,879
talk about our dreams.

88
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:42,079
Dreams?

89
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,040
Speak freely.

90
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,399
You see, I'm the kind of guy

91
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,160
who just wants to make it big.

92
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:48,360
I want to be rich.

93
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:50,079
You're too blunt!

94
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:51,720
Isn't that what we mean?

95
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:55,639
To succeed and get rich,

96
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:57,600
the best way

97
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,639
is to become a boss.

98
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,519
No, no, no!

99
00:05:03,399 --> 00:05:03,839
No, no, no!

100
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,879
No, no, no!

101
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:05,959
That's not what I meant.

102
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,240
That's exactly what you meant.

103
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:07,879
You're a good man.

104
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,800
Let me play you a tune.

105
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:09,800
No, no, no!

106
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:10,800
Get to the point.

107
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:15,279
Achieve your dreams with your own hands.

108
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,279
Good luck!

109
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:23,920
Wait, no...

110
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,519
Why am I so sleepy?

111
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,399
My three lords,

112
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:28,319
this is evidence from the Jingxi Mine Murder Case.

113
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,480
Witnesses and evidence are all here.

114
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:31,160
If there's no issue, I'll file it away.

115
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,079
Go ahead.

116
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:32,920
Wait.

117
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,480
What's he doing?

118
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,879
Flint.

119
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,000
It's just a stone.

120
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,319
Why's he treating it like a treasure?

121
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,360
What do you know?

122
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:52,319
This is called flint.

123
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,360
Flint.

124
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:55,600
This thing

125
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,439
comes from the Xishan Mine.

126
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,839
The stone used in the capital

127
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,639
all comes from the Xishan Mine.

128
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,279
Right.

129
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,000
Good, good, good.

130
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,639
It's time to show some real skill.

131
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,120
Greetings, Silver Guards.

132
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,639
Can this thing be forged?

133
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,240
It doesn't seem difficult.

134
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,319
I can have it made for you within a day.

135
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,439
Much obliged.

136
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,600
I'll come pick it up tomorrow.

137
00:06:36,439 --> 00:06:37,920
What's this mysterious thing you're forging?

138
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:39,480
A spear.

139
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,079
Who do you think you're fooling?

140
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,480
Like I've never seen a spear before?

141
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,519
Not the kind of spear you're thinking of.

142
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,759
Forget it, you wouldn't understand anyway.

143
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,639
Oh right, A Zheng.

144
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:48,759
After you head back tonight,

145
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,879
get me some sulfur,

146
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,079
saltpeter, and charcoal.

147
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:52,759
Don't let anyone find out.

148
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,199
What are you doing?

149
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,079
Who said you could—

150
00:07:08,319 --> 00:07:09,079
Greetings, Commander Geng.

151
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,040
Where's Ning Chen?

152
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:10,800
Re-re-reporting...

153
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,240
Reporting to Commander Geng, Ning Chen has arrived.

154
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,680
He arrived and went straight in.

155
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,920
Acting all secretive, who knows what he's up to.

156
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,199
Sounds like he's practicing something...

157
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:17,720
Practicing with a spear.

158
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,319
A spear?

159
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:18,920
A spear.

160
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:20,759
Ning Chen!

161
00:07:21,399 --> 00:07:22,839
Come out, I need you.

162
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,120
Get lost!

163
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,199
Don't bother me!

164
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,720
Has he gone rabid?

165
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,160
How dare he talk to me like that?

166
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,639
Does he know who I am?

167
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:36,720
Get out here!

168
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:39,160
I don't care who you are!

169
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,560
Whatever it is, it can wait!

170
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,879
I finally did it!

171
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:56,799
This...

172
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:12,559
Demons, ghosts, and black bull spirits!

173
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:15,480
By Lord Lao's command, obey at once!

174
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,360
Command, my foot!

175
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,120
Ning Chen!

176
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,200
What are you doing?

177
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:24,759
You—

178
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,360
Congratulations, everyone.

179
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:30,480
You're about to witness our Da Xuan

180
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,320
enter the age of firearms.

181
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,279
Have you gone rabid?

182
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,960
What on earth is a "firearm"?

183
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,600
He's gotten dangerously obsessed with his training.

184
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:40,440
You can't just practice with any random spear.

185
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,519
You call this a spear?

186
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,120
Where's the spearhead?

187
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,159
Who says without a spearhead

188
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:47,919
it can't kill?

189
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:53,600
Gentlemen.

190
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,240
Cover your ears.

191
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,639
Lord Geng,

192
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,240
how tough of you.

193
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:07,960
Lao Gao,

194
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,120
help me cover my ears.

195
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,559
Thanks a bunch, kind soul.

196
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,679
What'd you say? I can't hear you!

197
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:30,879
He said,

198
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,720
"Thank you."

199
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,320
"Eat rice."

200
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:36,120
Aren't we having buns for lunch? He said—

201
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,639
What on earth is this?

202
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,159
First a spark,

203
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:46,399
then a roar like a dragon.

204
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:47,720
This,

205
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:50,000
is the musket.

206
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,960
Why are you just mouthing words?

207
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:01,200
He said,

208
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:03,360
"This is a musket."

209
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:04,120
A musket?

210
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:13,840
Ning Zi,

211
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,919
where did this iron pellet come from?

212
00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:27,519
I'm asking,

213
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:30,799
where did this iron pellet come from?

214
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:31,679
Get it now?

215
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:41,879
On the battlefield,

216
00:11:42,279 --> 00:11:43,559
arrows leave a visible trail,

217
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,399
giving enemies time to react.

218
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,960
A musket fires

219
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:48,080
without a trace.

220
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,799
At close range,

221
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:51,399
it pierces armor.

222
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:53,559
Commander Geng truly has insight.

